      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are functional, the car shows noticeable signs of its age, including several minor scratches and dings on the exterior body panels. The interior is clean but exhibits visible wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. It has been maintained to keep it roadworthy, but a new owner should expect some upcoming minor cosmetic or mechanical refurbishments to bring it back to peak form.",
