      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a new home. It\u2019s been super reliable and is in solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a great car without the brand-new price tag. It runs like a dream and has been well-cared for. I'd love for you to come by and see it for yourself\u2014you're going to love how it drives!",
