    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. The chassis has been inspected for rear subframe integrity, and the suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior shows honest wear consistent with careful enthusiast ownership. Mechanically sound with documented VANOS servicing and valve adjustments, this E46 offers a pure analog driving experience without the compromise of modern electronic interference.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
