    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-maintained driver\u2019s car, offering a perfect blend of reliability and sophisticated style. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though a close inspection reveals the faint, honest character of the road\u2014such as minor stone chips on the lower front bumper that have been professionally touched up. Inside, the cabin feels remarkably fresh; the seats are supportive with no thinning or cracks in the material, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All electronic features, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, function exactly as they did when the car left the showroom. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, resulting in a smooth-shifting transmission and a quiet, responsive engine. The suspension remains tight and composed over bumps, and the tires have plenty of life remaining. This is a turnkey vehicle for someone who wants the prestige and performance of a high-end model without the 'new car' price tag.",
